# Priority
priority: optional

# Section
section: universe/otherosfs

# Descripción corta
shortdesc: "System-Wide configuration for Wine."

# Descipción larga, las lineas han de estar separadas por "\n "
longdesc: "This packages configures a unique installation of Wine for all users of system."

# Versión del paquete
version: 1.0.4

# Cambios en esta versión
changes:
    - Used new scripts to update root and user directories.
    - Fixed scripts to run when XDG variables are not defined.
    - Forced to reload Desktop menus after each wine execution.
    - Added kde-baseapps-bin | zenity to dependencies.
    - Added kdesudo | gksu to dependencies.
    - Support for gtk interfaces.
